Package com.geodrop.DropPay

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentDeliveryMessage
    Response to a ContentDeliveryMessage request
    ContentDeliveryMessage_Response
    Request used to send a content as a smart message free of charge for customer
    CustomerCheck
    Request used to return the full status of customer, if the port type is SUBSCRIPTION
    CustomerCheck_Response
    Response to a CustomerCheck request
    CustomerGoodbye
    Request used to unsubscribe a customer to a specific Port
    CustomerWelcome
    Request used to subscribe a customer to a specific Port
    CustomerWelcomeGoodbay_Response
    Response to a CustomerWelcome or a CustomerGoodbay request
    Listener
    Gives information about an event posted by DropPay
    Mno
    Indicates settings for which the payment port is enabled (see Mobile Network Code)
    Port
    Port configuration's properties
    PortChallenge
    Request used to challenge customer to confirm the telephone number in content provider initiated transaction
    PortChallenge_Response
    Response to a PortChallenge request
    PortChargeOnDemandPurchases
    Request used to charge customer with the previously defined price if port type is ONDEMAND
    PortChargePurchases_Response
    Response to a PortChargePurchases request
    PortChargeSubscriptionPurchases
    Request used to charge customer with the previously defined price if port type is SUBSCRIPTION
    PortDescriptor
    Request used to return the full Port configuration's properties
    PortDescriptor_Response
    Response to a PortDescriptor request
    PortTrigger
    Request used to charge all subscribed customers with the previously defined price
    PortTrigger_Response
    Response to a PortTrigger request
